      "rationale": "All experimental testing performed at a single crosshead displacement rate (5 mm/min) and ambient laboratory temperature (22 ± 2 degrees C). ASTM F1717 specifies a single quasi-static rate; no multi-rate study was conducted. This factor does not achieve the required level 3 due to the single test condition evaluated. Noted as a limitation; accepted given that F1717 is a standardised protocol and rate sensitivity for quasi-static titanium constructs is well-established in literature."
    },
