      "rationale": "Point-by-point equivalency table completed: screw OD (7.5 mm nominal, CMM-confirmed), rod diameter (5.5 mm), UHMWPE block dimensions per F1717 Annex A, crosshead displacement rate, ambient temperature, set-screw torque. All FEA inputs traceable to experimental measurements or specifications. Level 3 achieved."
