      "rationale": "The three QoIs map directly to ASTM F1717 reportable quantities and to the regulatory question of whether the non-cannulated construct meets the mechanical performance threshold established by the predicate device. Stiffness governs immediate post-operative stability; yield force governs failure risk; force at 40 mm displacement characterises post-yield reserve. All three are necessary and sufficient for the COU decision. Level 3 achieved."
