      "rationale": "Validation activities conducted on the exact non-cannulated 7.5 mm production design under the exact ASTM F1717 static compression-bending protocol specified in the COU. No surrogates or scaled models used in the primary validation. The corroborating cannulated dataset was noted as providing additional mechanistic confidence given the shared outer geometry and material; its use as a supplementary reference was assessed as appropriate by the team without formal examination of the hollow-core stress concentration difference that distinguishes cannulated from non-cannulated yield behavior. Level 3 achieved."
